{"type": "article", "id": 51120, "title": "这个内置音箱的浴室柜，灵感源自老式唱片机｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-14T22:59:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48445, "name": "Olympia Ceramica"}, {"id": 48446, "name": "Simplistyk"}, {"id": 48447, "name": "Gianluca Paludi"}, {"id": 48448, "name": "Martijn Koomen"}, {"id": 48449, "name": "Tadas Maksimovas"}, {"id": 23351, "name": "Tom Fereday"}, {"id": 22818, "name": "Vito Nesta"}, {"id": 48450, "name": "Christine Duell"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 238, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180315003924cB2fkAbv7HOLVQxm.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #4d4d4d; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #4d4d4d} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>LeviZen By Simplistyk</h3><p>加州设计团队 Simplistyk 最近在众筹网站 Kickstarter 上发布了一款水滴悬浮装置 LeviZen，似是要对抗地心引力，将水珠的上上下下全操控在自己手中。</p><p>设计团队通过高频声波的方式，创作出这台让水滴悬浮于半空中不坠落的装置，可以把它当作摆饰，放在办公桌、茶几或是书架上。它由细致的胡桃木与精密加工的铝材制成，悬浮装置的盒子上有三个复古风格的开关，分别是主电源开关、灯光开关和移动水滴上下方向的开关。另外还有一个大大的金属旋钮，能够调节 7 段功率，有点听收音机的感觉。</p><p>除了控制水滴悬浮之外，底座上还有两颗 LED 灯，打开灯后，灯光就会照射悬浮的水滴，使得水珠变成一个上下移动的光点。早鸟价 199 美元，<a href=\"https://www.damanwoo.com/node/91200\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803150040014tOlkHiYgzmFxIQX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004001nDqjgv1VbCLG8F96.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004001Nviw841M3jYrmZlx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803150040010DLZKqAJmvHjOdf1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004001nB6oJMGeZhq582ET.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004001lTo0XCAdBHq7p3Mf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Nessa Brush Spa by Christine Duell</h3><p>化妆刷用一段时间后会有很多螨虫、皮肤的油脂、死皮等，所以经常清洗化妆刷是很有必要的。最近，Christine Duell 在众筹网站 Indiegogo 上发布了一款化妆刷自动清洁器 NESSA，另配有散粉刷、粉底刷、腮红刷、眼影刷、眼影混合刷、皱纹刷六支市面上常用的化妆刷。</p><p>这个清洁器可以一次性完成从清洁到干燥的程序。它的外观看起来像一个小型的饮水机或者毛笔架，一次性可以清洁三支不同的化妆刷，清洁完成后，化妆刷自动弹起脱离化妆垫，风扇自动出风干燥刷毛。早鸟价 149 美元，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/nessa-brush-spa-makeup#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004031SRcNeFktx9wKTEbq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749640\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004404AUeCyfS63X5hT42p.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560538\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004407NUafW6P5Q48FyBxY.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562992\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004407ctoR6MIbdUYw4eG8.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004408JTft6zsuI4PnZ5Me.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561905\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803150044085g9r3YhSQtdpERKq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563107\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Grand Tour Collection by Vito Nesta</h3><p>米兰设计师 Vito Nesta 推出了一套名为 Grand Tour 的作品，分为三个系列，表现的都是巴西与日本的文化艺术元素。</p><p>Las Palmas 系列盘子表面绿色的棕榈树反映了巴西殖民地文化，与金属光泽边缘形成了鲜明的对比。Natsumi 盘子系列是深红色和亮蓝色的组合，表现的是人们所建的寺庙为童话般的自然世界所包围的感觉。</p><p>Wagasa 系列地毯采用了日本传统雨伞的特点，由竹子与米纸制作而成，并将其转化为装饰元素，用彩色的几何图案构成不同款式的纸扇。Anatomica 陶瓷系列，是一组经典形状的手的原型，装饰效果很好。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004451RUHZW3n9ojMiax0X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004453WXj3zIp4ZH2K0fwG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004453QlaSvFmtKTz41j78.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803150044573y0juDTS5cdVxqaY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004458tMB6RF1pNUisT9ZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/vito-nesta-grand-tour-brazilian-japanese-03-12-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>DesignByThem Collection by Tom Fereday</h3><p>澳大利亚设计师 Tom Fereday 为本土设计品牌 DesignByThem 推出了 Bow 系列新品，包括一个双座长凳，和一把拱形靠背的椅子，混合了曲线和直线，突出了木材的纹理，也可选择添加软垫座垫。售价 1595 澳元起，<a href=\"https://www.designbythem.com/collections/bow\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803150046486MnU3HGSl7yKQVLx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.854688\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004648af0nBdIytQ4K59cs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004648zplFSq1v8TDoAM7x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.635938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004649DvgV0NGqKclUCBkS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.805469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004649uqEC4aNwmzfbOLyn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.860938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004649ImrHbS6NFaTc5tEi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pi Bike by Martijn Koomen &amp; Tadas Maksimovas</h3><p>3 月 14 日是圆周率日（Pi Day），为了庆祝这一天，设计师 Martijn Koomen 和 Tadas Maksimovas 以马来西亚艺术家 Tang Yau Hoong 创作的 π 型自行车插图为灵感，带来了这款 π 符号形状的自行车，手工制作的碳纤维框架，用大胆醒目的白色勾勒出 π 的形状，充满未来感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004742eHzmhMyOEtAx6wTc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004742v0xI2U8P9rqGOJQc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004743chtFknx6sdTlvWu5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803150047431InkE4ucjRqSsHhY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004746Jp8dVyhPTCcOXkzj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004747M4UZqgAtE1dsixHB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/the-pi-bike-is-a-fixed-gear-bicycle-in-the-shape-of-the-pi-symbol/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Vinyl Inspired Bathroom Sinks by Gianluca Paludi</h3><p>如果你喜欢乙烯树脂，又很怀旧老式唱片机的时代，Gianluca Paludi 设计的这款融合了水槽、洗手台和 DJ 设置的浴室系列，可能会很对你的胃口。</p><p>这是意大利高端卫浴洁具品牌 Olympia Ceramica 推出的新品，水龙头就像拿着手写笔的手臂，嵌入式水槽像是唱机转盘，“转盘上的调节音量按钮”用于调节水压和温度。水槽的木制底座内置有一个收纳抽屉，抽屉内藏有蓝牙控制的音响。另有承担额外收纳功能的钢化玻璃架、毛巾杆和皮箱。</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004831DCzxiN8MPycgIKru.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004831NAoIKBF4XblH2hD3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803150048312Eehl1zaqBcr5v3f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004831sM4aZTkeGL8QhBSd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004832Dg2iTQ7AsOheErSn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180315004832XYsy96Oknp4BF2H3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}